records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Incorrect heading levels announced
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce heading level as 2 for the 'Saguache County Government Accessibility Statement' and 'Accessibility' headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Visual list not defined as list
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce 'List with 11' items for the ordered list under the 'Digital Accessibility Efforts and Saguache County Digital Accessibility Transition Plan' heading.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Visual headings not defined as headings
records.Expected Result:
The screen reader should announce the following visual headings as headings at level 4:
1. Introduction & Purpose
2. Scope
3. Accessibility Standards
4. Current Accessibility Assessment
5. Remediation Plan
6. Implementation Timeline
7. Roles & Responsibilities Accessibility Coordinator
8. Training & Education
9. Procurement & Development Policy
10. Monitoring, Maintenance & feedback
11. Contact Information

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Visual list not defined as list under the 'Hours of Operation' heading
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce 'List with 9' items for the visual list under the 'Hours of Operation' heading.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Visual list not defined as list under the 'Social Services' text
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce 'Lst with 2 items' for the list under the 'Social Services' list item.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: Asterisk symbol announced separately
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the first asterisk symbol together with the '* Saguache County Land Use will NOT be going to Crestone until a new location is determined**' text.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Administrations: Incorrect heading level announced
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce heading level as 2 for the 'Staff' and 'Address' headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Incorrect heading levels announced
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce heading level as 2 for the 'Accessibility' headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Incorrect implementation of list
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the correct list as a list with 2 items.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Incorrect role announced for links
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the role as 'Link' for the 'Learn More' link.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home:  Next/Previous buttons are missing accessible name
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the label as 'Next slide' and 'Previous slide' buttons.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Label is not announced for the close button
records.Expected Result: Screen reader should announce the label as 'Close' for the button.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: The search result not announced automatically
records.Expected Result:
The screen reader should announce the 'No matches found' search result automatically.
Additionally, the screen reader should announce the 'Searching....' notification automatically.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Unnecessary text 'table' is announced for the search field
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the text Table' for the search field.

records.Issue Title: Other A11y: Home: Visual label is not provided for the 'Select Language' combobox
records.Expected Result: The visible label should be present for the 'Select language' combobox.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Unnecessary carousel region is defined
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should not announce the carousel region for the main region.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Saguache county logo missing alternative text
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the alternative text for the logo image as 'Saguache County, Colorado government logo'.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Lengthy link text announced for links
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the link 'Saguache County Weather' as a link.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Incorrect heading level announced for text
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the correct heading level 2 for the text 'Saguache county weather'.

records.Issue Title: Chrome+NVDA: Home: Purpose is not announce for the links
records.Expected Result:
The screen reader should announce the correct purpose for the following links.
-Moon link
-Rainy Cloud link

records.Issue Title: Chrome+NVDA: Home: Link is announced twice for link text
records.Expected Result: Screen reader should announce the role 'link' once for the link text.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Home: Banner landmark missing on the page
records.Expected Result: Banner landmark should be present on the page.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Administration Documents & Applications: Unnecessary heading is announced
records.Expected Result: The table headers 'Title' and 'Last Modified' are unnecessarily announced as headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Administration Documents & Applications: Table is not announced for tabular content
records.Expected Result: The table should be announced for the 'Documents & Applications Information' table.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Saguache County Sales Tax Grant: Unnecessary heading is announced
records.Expected Result: Text 'If you have any questions ...co.gov' should be announced by the screen reader as plain text instead of a heading.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Adopted Budgets: Image link missing accessible name
records.Expected Result: The image link associated with links like 'UPDATE 2025 Draft Budget' should have alternate text or should not be focused.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Adopted Budgets: Links announced insufficiently
records.Expected Result: Links like '2024_mill_levy.pdf' should be announced with file size, e.g., '2024_mill_levy.pdf 681.43 KB'.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Adopted Budgets: Multiple lists are announced for expandable buttons
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce a single list of 8 items in one go.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Assesor Documents: Unnecessary heading is announced
records.Expected Result: The table headers 'Title' and 'Last Modified' are unnecessarily announced as headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Assesor Documents: Table is not announced for tabular content
records.Expected Result: The table should be announced for the 'Documents & Applications Information' table.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Assessor: Incorrect heading hierarchy
records.Expected Result:
The following headings should be marked up under level 2 instead of 3:
-Staff
-Address
-Saguache County Parcel Viewer
-EagleWeb Property Search
-Valuation Increases Expected for most County Property Owners
-2025 Notices of Valuation
-2025 SAGUACHE COUNTY REAPPRAISAL
-MASS APPRAISAL

records.Issue Title: Other A11y: Assessor: Image of text is used to convey the information
records.Expected Result: Image of text should not be used for the image to convey the information on the page. In this case, the information should be conveyed as normal text instead of the image of text.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Audits: Links announced insufficiently
records.Expected Result: Links like '2022_financial_statements.pdf' should be announced with file size, e.g., '2022_financial_statements.pdf 1.81MB'.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Audits: Multiple lists are announced for expandable buttons
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce a single list of 6 items in one go for the expandable buttons.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Board of County Commissioners Agendas: Incorrect heading hierarchy
records.Expected Result:
The following headings should be marked up under level 2 instead of 3:
-Saguache County Board of County Commissioners Preliminary Special Saguache County Board of Housing Meeting and Work Session Agenda Tuesday, July 29, 2025
-Commissioners May Attend

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Board of County Commissioners Agendas: Table implemented incorrectly
records.Expected Result:
Case 1. Plain text should not be included in the table. The table should be tagged from 'Decision'.
Case 2. The first column should have a table header.
Case 3. Table caption must be provided.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: BOCC Documents: Unnecessary heading is announced
records.Expected Result: The table headers 'Title' and 'Last Modified' are unnecessarily announced as headings.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: BOCC Documents: Table is not tagged for tabular content
records.Expected Result: The table should be announced for the 'Documents & Applications Information' table.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Land Uses: Insufficient alternative for map image
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce complete information about locations, Hospitals, schools and '100 years of plan'.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Land Uses: Incorrect heading level announced
records.Expected Result: The screen reader should announce the correct heading level 2 for the content ' Download the Hi-Resolution PDF File:&n'.

records.Issue Title: Screen Reader: Child Support Services: List not announced for items
records.Expected Result: The list of 5 items should be announced by the screen reader for the items present under the 'Child Support Service' heading.

records.Issue Title: Other A11y: Commissioners: Information conveyed via sensory characterstics
records.Expected Result: Information should be conveyed in a way that does not rely solely on sensory characteristics, such as sound, sight, or touch, and should be perceivable by users through multiple modes of interaction, provide an alternative method to perceive the information, such as text description or adjustable visual cues.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Home: The temperature text like '41F' fails the color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The temperature text like '41F' is a textual information and in regular font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the text should be at least 4.5:1.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Home: The link text 'here to download' fails the color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The 'here to download' link text is a textual information and is in regular font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the text should be at least 4.5:1.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: 'Online form' link text fails color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The 'online form' link text is a textual information and is in regular font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the text should be at least 4.5:1.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Accessibility at Saguache County Government: 'SCG Website Accessibility and Support Form' link texts fails color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The 'SCG Website Accessibility and Support Form' link texts are textual information and are in regular font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the text should be at least 4.5:1.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Home: The large text 'Saguache County Government' fails the color contrast ratio due to irregular background
records.Expected Result: The text 'Saguache County Government' is a textual information and in large font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the large text should be at least 3.0:1.
records.Dev Comments:
Owned by P15r 
The image with text fails color contrast. The client needs to update it with a background that meets the 4.5:1 ratio, which may require extra design and development effort.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Home: The link text 'Click here to download' fails the color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The 'Click here to download' link text is a textual information and is in regular font size, so as per the WCAG, the color contrast ratio of the text should be at least 4.5:1.

records.Issue Title: Color Contrast: Home: The Sunny weather icon fails the color contrast ratio
records.Expected Result: The 'Sunny' weather icon is a graphical object, so as per WCAG the color contrast ratio of the icon should be at least 3.0:1 against the adjacent colors.
